00:19.483 --> 00:20.344
Yeah.

00:21.366 --> 00:23.789
You really read the book, didn't you?

00:23.809 --> 00:25.271
Pleasure to deal with it, Nick.

00:25.291 --> 00:27.795
Thank you.

00:27.815 --> 00:28.396
