01:36.669 --> 01:38.592
I'm either going to tell it or I'm not going to tell it.

01:38.612 --> 01:38.992
You got it.

01:39.373 --> 01:39.673
That's it.

01:40.054 --> 01:41.155
That's it, exactly what you said.

01:41.175 --> 01:42.437
