02:00.702 --> 02:01.163
They were...

02:02.712 --> 02:05.817
the ones I was most anxious about and really waited for.

02:05.957 --> 02:10.986
I actually waited to see what my wife and my daughters would say about it.

02:11.006 --> 02:18.478
And one daughter kept putting it off, putting it off, because she was either afraid of it or whatever the hell, and she liked it 90%.

02:20.261 --> 02:21.283
My sons read it right away.

02:22.305 --> 02:23.026
I have three sons.

02:23.046 --> 02:24.469
They read it right away.

02:24.489 --> 02:25.470
One son made the index.

02:27.774 --> 02:28.956
You mentioned also I love

02:30.117 --> 02:47.483
Again, the picture, there's a picture in there, the clichÃ©, there's a picture worth a thousand words, where you show that picture of the group, this bold, zealous, revolutionary group, and you see a bunch of bored, pissed off people sitting there.

02:47.503 --> 02:48.205
